-body_bg); color: var(--body_color); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: var(--font_size);">. So let us continue to </span><span style="color: var(--body_color); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: var(--font_size); background-color: rgb(253, 235, 242);">support </span><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: var(--body_color); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: var(--font_size);">each other, uplift each other, and empower each other, not just on this day, but every day. Happy International Women's Day!</span></div><div><br></div><div><br></div></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1654090644203" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1654090644203" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-sm" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1653641854799" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1653641854799" data-layout-lg="3+9" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="3+9" data-layout-sm="3+9" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-3 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653641854829" data-id="1653641854829"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1653641932709" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1653641932709" data-resolution="640x640" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/494ac25e-0853-4776-89b0-2a7b2e3bd713/-/format/auto/-/preview/640x640/-/quality/lighter/1080x1080-Pink.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="40%" data-height="auto" title=""